title: Android 13 preview for the Oppo Find X5 Pro is now available
content:
Google I/O usually marks the time when the latest version of Android graduates from its early previews and starts the journey through betas towards public availability. Ahead of today’s keynote, one of Google’s partners is jumping on board, with Oppo launching its first Android 13 preview for the Find X5 Pro.

more…

The post Android 13 preview for the Oppo Find X5 Pro is now available appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: The Oppo Find X5 Pro is one of the first devices to launch an Android 13 preview, with a developer preview based on Beta 1 available now.
